表格停机记录表的代码预览

if exists (select 1
from sysobjects
where id = object_id('DeviceRealStatus')
and type = 'U')
drop table DeviceRealStatus
go

/*==============================================================*/
/* Table: DeviceRealStatus */
/*==============================================================*/
create table DeviceRealStatus (
ID int identity(1,1),
ClientIP varchar(50) null,
DispatchNo varchar(50) null,
StatusID int null,
StartCardID varchar(20) null,
EndCardID varchar(20) null,
DeviceStatus char(2) null,
Start_Date datetime null,
End_Date datetime null,
LastUpdateDate datetime null,
StartEmpID varchar(20) null,
EndEmpID varchar(20) null,
constraint PK_DEVICEREALSTATUS primary key (ID)
)
ON [PRIMARY]
END
go
